examples.en: He spoke with a tremulous voice.
He is tremulous to all the influences.
With drooping heads and tremulous tails, they mashed their way through the thick mud. (Ch. Dickens)
examples.ru: С опущенными мордами и дрожащими хвостами они тащились по густой грязи.

examples.en: She spoke timidly in a tremulous voice.
She opened the letter with tremulous hands.
